  <mainDescription>&lt;p>&#xD;
    The organization should have or will develop a safety culture, based establishment, execution and maintenance of a&#xD;
    specific set of rules and processes that comply with ISO 26262.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Details of the requirements for this task are detailed in ISO 26262, volume 2, clause 5.4.2 The user is also&#xD;
    recommended to examine appendix B, ISO 26262 volume 2, tables B1, examples of leading indicators of safety culture and&#xD;
    B2 Examples of trailing indicators of a safety culture.&#xD;
&lt;/p></mainDescription>
  <purpose>To ensure that the organization carrying out the work has the background and basic skill set required to carry out item&#xD;
development to be compliant with ISO 26262.</purpose>
</org.eclipse.epf.uma:TaskDescription>
